            <title data-rh="true">AI Governance In Action: Harvey LAB Benchmark Puts Claude, Gemini, and ChatGPT to the Test</title>
            
            <meta data-rh="true" name="theme-color" content="#ffffff"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:type" content="article"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:title" content="AI Governance In Action: Harvey LAB Benchmark Puts Claude, Gemini, and ChatGPT to the Test"/><meta data-rh="true" name="twitter:title" content="AI Governance In Action: Harvey LAB Benchmark Puts Claude, Gemini, and ChatGPT to the Test"/><meta data-rh="true" name="description" content="HarveyAI just dropped LAB — a tough new open-source benchmark testing frontier models (GPT, Claude, Gemini) on real partner-level legal work. The results are humbling: top models pass under 10% of tasks. Discover jagged intelligence, cost/latency trade-offs, and practical guidance for law firms adopting AI safely. All from AI Governance, Ethics &amp; Leadership. The premier destination for AI Governance &amp; Responsible AI."/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:description" content="HarveyAI just dropped LAB — a tough new open-source benchmark testing frontier models (GPT, Claude, Gemini) on real partner-level legal work. The results are humbling: top models pass under 10% of tasks. Discover jagged intelligence, cost/latency trade-offs, and practical guidance for law firms adopting AI safely. All from AI Governance, Ethics &amp; Leadership. The premier destination for AI Governance &amp; Responsible AI."/><meta data-rh="true" name="twitter:description" content="HarveyAI just dropped LAB — a tough new open-source benchmark testing frontier models (GPT, Claude, Gemini) on real partner-level legal work. The results are humbling: top models pass under 10% of tasks. Discover jagged intelligence, cost/latency trade-offs, and practical guidance for law firms adopting AI safely. All from AI Governance, Ethics &amp; Leadership. The premier destination for AI Governance &amp; Responsible AI."/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:image" content="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PFHc!,w_1200,h_675,c_fill,f_jpg,q_auto